    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously cared for since day one. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and there are absolutely no scratches, dents, or imperfections to be found. Inside, the leather upholstery remains supple and looks as if it has never been sat in, while all electronic features and mechanical components function perfectly. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been kept in a climate-controlled environment and serviced exclusively at authorized dealerships. A complete service history is available, confirming its pristine status.",
